+ Work with\nComplex Types
++ ARRAY
+++ Ordered sequences
++++_ Same-type values
++++_ tags ARRAY<STRING>
++++_ Access: tags[0]
++ MAP
+++ Key-value pairs
++++_ Dynamic keys
++++_ properties MAP<STRING,STRING>
++++_ Access: properties['key']
-- STRUCT
--- Named fields
----_ Nested records
----_ STRUCT<field:type,...>
-- Use Cases
---_ ARRAY: product tags, categories
---_ MAP: flexible attributes
---_ STRUCT: nested objects
@endmindmap
